 #prime number
#number which divisible by one and itself except 1
   1
   
#number which is having exactly two factors
  1xxx 2 3 4 5 6 7 8

  prime number starts from 2
  1--1
  2--1,2
  3--1,3
  4--1,2,4
  5,-1,5
  6-1,2,3,6
  7-1,7
--->     15---->
----> 15%1  15%2  15%3  ....      15%15
    ----1----15--loop
    1500---
    1500%1---------------------1500%1500
    it will take time

